channel.description:
It was not ment to be good so don't tell me how horrible it is, since im well aware of that. I was really bored and saw a picture of a pacman thing on fb so i thought of making a pacman sword :P so here it is. Once again it was not ment to be good i was just testing the idea of it :3 poly overkill on some parts.. ik. PLEASE DON'T HATE. PS I WILL RELEASE IT LATER.
